{"article_id":"VMzbrrq3MFpweU5U","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"NORTH LAS VEGAS , Nev. -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"In a testy exchange with Ed Henry of Fox News on Tuesday , Hillary Rodham Clinton defended her handling of the server","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that hosted the personal email account","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"she exclusively used as secretary of state","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"and reiterated","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"that she did not receive any emails","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"that were marked as classified .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"\" Ed , you ' re not listening to me , \"","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"Mrs. Clinton said","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"after the cable news reporter asked another follow-up question about the email issue .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"She said","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"the process","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"of investigating what was potentially classified","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"would be playing out the same way","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"had she used an official government account .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"\" This is part of the ordinary process , \"","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"Mrs. Clinton said .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"\" Everybody is acting","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"like it ' s the first time","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"it ' s ever happened .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"It happens all the time . \"","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"When pressed as to whether she took responsibility for the controversy","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"her private email use has prompted ,","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"Mrs. Clinton said ,","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"\" I regret this has become such a cause célèbre ,","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"but that does not change the facts . \"","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"\" I know","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"there ' s a certain level of sort of anxiety or interest in this ,","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"but the facts are the facts , \"","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"she said .","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"Mrs. Clinton has fielded questions about the email controversy at almost every stop on the campaign","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"since she announced her candidacy for the presidency in April ,","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"but the exchange on Tuesday was particularly tense .","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"At one point Mr. Henry asked Mrs. Clinton about an NBC News report","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"that the Federal Bureau of Investigation may be able to recover some of the messages on the server","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"and whether she had tried to wipe the server clean","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"before handing it over to the F.B.I .","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"That exchange follows :","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"Mr. Henry :","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"Did you try to wipe the entire server ?","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"Mrs. Clinton :","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"My personal emails are my personal business , right ?","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"We went through a painstaking process","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"and turned over 55,000 pages of anything","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"we thought","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"could be work-related .","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"Under the law , that decision is made by the official .","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"I was the official .","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"I made those decisions ,","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"and","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"as I just said","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"over 1,200 of the emails have already been deemed not work-related .","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"All","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"I can tell you","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"is","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"in retrospect","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"had I used a government account","depth":14},{"id":57,"text":"and I ' d said :","depth":14},{"id":58,"text":"\" You know what ,","depth":15},{"id":59,"text":"let ' s release everything .","depth":15},{"id":60,"text":"Let ' s let everybody in America see what I did for four years , \"","depth":14},{"id":61,"text":"we would have the same arguments .","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"Mr. Henry :","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"Answer the question .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"Did you try to wipe the whole server ?","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"You didn ' t answer the question .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"Mrs. Clinton :","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"I don ' t .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"I have no idea ,","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"that ' s why I turned it over .","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"Mr. Henry :","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"You were the official in charge of it .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"Did you wipe the server ?","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"Mr. Henry :","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"I don ' t know .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"You know","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"how it works digitally .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"Mrs. Clinton :","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"I don ' t know","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"how it works digitally at all .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"Mr. Henry :","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"So you didn ' t try ?","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"You did not try ?","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"Mrs. Clinton :","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"Ed , I know","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"you want to make a point","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"and I can just repeat what I said .","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"Mrs. Clinton :","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"In order to be as cooperative as possible","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"we have turned over the server .","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"They can do whatever they want to with the server","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"to figure out what is there and not there .","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"That ' s for the people","depth":15},{"id":93,"text":"investigating it","depth":15},{"id":94,"text":"to figure out .","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"But we have turned over everything","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"that was work-related ,","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"every single thing .","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"Personal stuff , we did not .","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"I had no obligation","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"to do so","depth":13},{"id":101,"text":"and did not .","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"After that , Mrs. Clinton started to depart the gymnasium here ,","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"where she had just concluded a wide-ranging town hall meeting .","depth":6},{"id":104,"text":"An NBC News reporter shouted ,","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"\" Is this an indication","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"that this issue isn ' t going to go away for the remainder of your campaign ? \"","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"But by then a visibly irritated Mrs. Clinton had already made her way toward the door .","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"She threw a wristy wave goodbye to the press corps","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"as she said ,","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"\" Nobody talks to me about it other than you guys . \"","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":221,"left":0,"right":220,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":220,"left":139,"right":219,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":139,"left":130,"right":138,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":116,"right":129,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":113,"right":115,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":113,"left":1,"right":112,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":4,"right":114,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":114,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":118,"right":128,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":7,"right":117,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":124,"right":127,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":